snippet.title: Shahleena
snippet.description:
Yo! This is my wee lil beauty channel about generally everything....you guessed it...beauty related! Whether it be reviews, hauls or random beauty chat you will find something here to inform and maybe mildly amuse you. 
I give honest reviews based on my own experiences using a particular product. If I have been sent something for review I will state it however, I am not influenced to say anything other than the truth.
I hope that you enjoy my channel and remember that beauty, makeup and everything in between, is just for fun - life is so much more fun with a little bit of colour
